            <div n="1">
                <p>
                    <milestone n="1r" unit="folio" facs="2"/>
                    <lb n="1"/>|| śrīmahāgaṇapataye namaḥ ||
                </p>
                <l xml:id="YS1.1">|| atha yogānuśāsanam ||</l>
                <p xml:id="YS1.1c">athety ayam adhikārārthaḥ || yogānuśāsanaṃ śāstram adhikṛtam || śrīrāma || <pb n="2r"/><lb n="1"/>veditavyaṃ | yogaḥ samādhiḥ sa ca sārvabhaumaḥ cittasya dharmaḥ | kṣiptaṃ <subst>m<del>u</del><add>ū</add></subst>ḍhaṃ vikṣiptam ekāgraṃ niruddham iti cittabhūmayaḥ | tatra vikṣipte cetasi vikṣepopasarjjanī<lb n="2"/>bhūtaḥ samādhir na yogapakṣe varttate || <pb n="2v" facs="2"/><lb n="1"/>yas tv ekāgre cetasi sadbhūtam arthaṃ pradyotayati kṣiṇoti ca kleśān karmabaṃdhanāni ślathayati nirodham abhumukhaṃ karoti sa saṃprajñāto yoga ity ākhyāyate | sa <lb n="2"/>ca vitarkānugato vicārānugata ānaṃdānugato 'smitānugata ity upariṣṭān na vedayiṣyāmaḥ | sarvavṛttinirodhatve tv asaṃprajñātaḥ samādhiḥ | tasya lakṣaṇā<lb n="3"/>bhidhitsayedaṃ sūtraṃ pravavṛte |</p>
